{
  "texts": [
    "We are writing an integral here for notational convenience, but it is actually a sum over pixels.",
    "There are several possible ways to go about solving for s(α).",
    "One can assume a parametric form for s(β) and fit for the parameters by minimizing χ 2.",
    "Alternatively, one can adopt a basis set for s(β) and fit for the coefficients in that basis set by minimizing χ 2.",
    "Birrer et al. (2015) present a suitable basis set for doing so (shapelets), while Galan et al. (2021) consider wavelets."
  ]
}